name: Memory Muncher
description:
Once upon a time there was a thread named Mem. Mem was having a lovely day out in the ram when suddenly the Ram went crazy! "It's coming!" the other programs screamed "Don't let it get you!". Help Mem dash out of the ram and back to their user program space in the page file away from the ram!

Each level gets incrementally harder. I'd be surprised if somebody could beat level 5.

Use the wasd keys to move or use the touch controls for mobile.

Make sure not to touch the other programs or it will slow you down!
